      "rationale": "Test sample characterization beyond the documented blood lot properties (hematocrit, MCV) is scoped out at MRL 2. Three independent blood lots were used across the validation experiments; inter-lot variability was within the measurement uncertainty budget. Gradation 1 satisfied."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
