      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/input-equivalency-mrl2",
      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters between validation and COU configurations is scoped out at MRL 2 per the factor applicability matrix. Documented comparison of validation vs. COU boundary conditions (flow rates, speeds, fluid properties) confirms alignment within the five assessed operating points. The coverage gap at the extreme operating point is captured under Relevance of Validation Activities. Gradation 1 satisfied."
